Here is the updated code.
To personalize the experience while acknowledging ownership, I have added a **User Profile banner** in the header. It explicitly notes that the system is licensed/belongs to **Prince Akuaku**, but features a **"Logged in as:" selector** where you can dynamically enter or change the current operator's name.
The application will immediately update the header greetings and greeting states to reflect whoever is currently tracking their packages.
